Linux OS
#Within a terminal, enter the following:
ssh username@hpc.usd.edu
#You will then be prompted to enter a password which should be the same as your myusd password:
username@hpc.usd.edu's password:passwordhere

Mac OS
#Access the terminal, HardDrive, Applications, Utilities, Terminal
#Within a terminal, enter the following:
ssh username@hpc.usd.edu
#YOuwill then be prompted to enter a password which should be the same as your myusd password:
username@hpc.usd.edu's password:passwordhere

